📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels

Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico
@roth.azulik @byroth_

node.text:
Has Mallorca crossed your mind lately? ✈️ If yes, Hotel Can Ferrereta, is where you need to be when visiting one of Spain's Balearic Islands! 🇪🇸

This 17th-century mansion has been turned into a 5-star hotel brimming with charm to make you fall in love with the town it's located in. From the gorgeous rooms and property grounds, you'll definitely feel like a local. The hotel lovingly preserves its art, history, and culture through its decors, ambiance, and true Mallorcan hospitality. ❤️

💡 BH tip: In need of a moment to explore the upmarket rural town of Santanyí? Go on bike tours of the town or head on to their beaches to soak up some Mallorcan sun. 🌅 You can also visit their local art galleries and join wine tours for an unforgettable experience! 🍷

Have you been to Mallorca? What are your recommendations for first-time visitors?

📍 @hotelcanferrereta, Balears, Spain

Swimming in mid-air with @hobopeeba. 😎 Connecting both Embassy Gardens and Legacy Building, this world-famous London attraction has captured the world's attention as the first ever Sky Pool with gorgeous, unobstructed views of the city. 🏙

node.text:
This is Amanruya: idyllic, chic, and a break from the usual. Imagine strolling in a village-like property, with the scent of pine trees melding with the Aegean sea breeze. ✨

Craving Turkish and Mediterranean meals made from locally sourced ingredients? Decide if you'll be enjoying it poolside, by the beach, in their Anatolian dining pavilion, or in the comfort of your own room! You can never run out of choices here. 😎

If you're the type to go all-in for wellness, Amanruya will definitely give you the most amazing pampering with unforgettable views! Think massages and mani-pedis overlooking the sea. 💅🏼 Ever had pampering with views of the sea? Would you want to experience that in Amanruya? 💆🏼

📍 @amanruya, Bodrum, Turkey

Aesthetic feels brought to you by @admbrs. 😍 Experience Art Nouveau grandeur in Splendid Palas Hotel Istanbul as you walk through their luxuriously designed interiors with rooms facing the city or the Marmara Sea. 📸 @admbrs

Fall in love with all things French with @lumadeline at Le Meurice in Paris. 🇫🇷 This reel is enough to make us all wistful for the Parisian experience, doesn't it? Le Meurice is what the Parisian experience is all about: divine food, timeless fashion, romance, luxury, and dreamy aesthetics. 😍

Feeling extra chic? Book the Belle Étoile Penthouse Suite. Nothing like French elegance to get you in Parisian time and mood. ❤️

Have you visited France? What is your recommendation when exploring Paris?

📽️ @lumadeline
📍 @lemeuriceparis
🎶 Paris Cafe Society - Memories of Paris

Relaxing with @bomkanari and @iverp in their modernized fisherman's cabin in Lofoten. 😍 Hattvika Lodge gives you an authentic Lofoten experience with their hillside and seaside cabins. In the mood for adventure? The lodge can arrange various activities for you such as ski trips, a Northern lights safari, and the legendary Lofoten fishing! 🎣

Once you are in Lofoten, take a stroll under the "midnight sun". Empty streets and blue skies at midnight are sure to make you feel like you're in another world!

Have you been to Norway? What was your favorite part of your trip? 😍 

📸 @bomkanari and @iverp
📍 @hattvikalodge, Ballstad, Norway
